===Verb===
{{cmn-verb|s|pin=jiànshì|pint=jian4shi4|tra=鑑識|sim=鑑识|rs=金05}}

# to closely examine; to perform a forensic examination
#: [[这]][[只]][[明朝]][[的]][[陶瓷]][[花瓶]][[请]][[你]]'''鉴识'''。
#: ''Please '''examine''' this Ming vase (and let me know your professional opinion about its authenticity, origin etc).''

====Usage notes====
*Used for situations in which a close examination using scientific or forensic techniques is required (such as in archeology).

